### List all bank transfer payments (default: 20 most recent)
GET http://localhost:8000/bank-payments

### List bank payments filtered by status
GET http://localhost:8000/bank-payments?status=EXECUTED

### List bank payments filtered by transfer type
GET http://localhost:8000/bank-payments?payment_type=sepa_credit

### List bank payments filtered by currency
GET http://localhost:8000/bank-payments?currency=EUR

### List bank payments filtered by IBAN country
GET http://localhost:8000/bank-payments?iban_country=ES

### List bank payments filtered by VAT number
GET http://localhost:8000/bank-payments?vat_number=B12345678

### List bank payments with multiple filters
GET http://localhost:8000/bank-payments?status=EXECUTED&currency=EUR&limit=5

### List bank payments with pagination (page 2)
GET http://localhost:8000/bank-payments?limit=10&offset=10

### Simulate bank transfer payments (from recent internal payments)
POST http://localhost:8000/bank-payments/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

### Simulate orphan bank transfer payments (no matching internal payment)
### These produce `missing_internal` after reconciliation runs
POST http://localhost:8000/bank-payments/simulate-orphan?count=3
Content-Type: application/json
